    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-802e-8718-f14a734ba9f2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Traditional BKT has two-learning states and the authors propose a third learning state. This means that they define the learning process into 3 sections. This small change to BKT shows superior results in comparison with BKT both in quantitative and qualitative terms.  ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-802e-8718-f14a734ba9f2",
